.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, hot-chocolate, lemonade, milk, mirinda, water
There are 7 different nationalities: italian, russian, nigerian, thai, canadian, polish, pakistani
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: tennis, biathlon, parkour, volleyball, handball, snowboarding, sailing
The people use 7 different means of transport: roller, taxi, helicopter, skateboard, snowmobile, car, boat
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is handball is the thai##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the russian is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 5. the italian is on the right of the pakistani##1
 6. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person driving the boat is on the right of the canadian##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the boat and the polish##2
 9. the canadian is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is the person drinking milk##1
12. the person drinking milk is the person driving the roller##1
13. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the nigerian##1
14. the polish is the person driving the helicopter##1
15. the person driving the car is on the left of the pakistani##1
16. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
17. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the nigerian##1
18. the person drinking water is on the right of the canadian##1
19. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

